item.title: NextGen Medizin
item.description: <kbd>2025</kbd></br> NextGen – Clinic.Research.Teaching.Life. is a newly launched initiative advocating for the clinical and research Mittelbau—practicing physicians, scientists, postdocs, and lecturers—within the Medical Faculty Council. Our mission: to amplify their influence on training, research infrastructure, and working conditions. We drive change through proactive dialogue, low-threshold funding, structured mentoring, and flexible career support tailored to today’s clinical-academic demands

item.title: Austrian Medical Students' Association
item.description: <kbd>2020</kbd></br> AMSA advocates for all medical students in Austria on a national and international level, since 1951 founding member of IFMSA, development and design of new Website in 2020, needs analysis, feedback rounds, project planning and timeline, sites: home, projects, become active, SCs, Exchange, LCs, International, Advocacy, about, Analytics, News, Events.

item.title: Students Union at the Sigmund Freud University Vienna
item.description: <kbd>2020</kbd></br> The ÖH SFU is the elected student body advocate for the interests of >5000 Students, act as the students’ political representation as well as offering services and hosting events, development of new Website and creation of new Corporate Identity, Sites including: Services, About, Contact, as well as SEO, Analytics with over 100 Visitors/day

item.title: Fachschaft Medizin Tübingen
item.description: <kbd>2018</kbd></br> FSMED is the student body of the faculty for medicine representing over >2500 students of the medical faculty of the University of Tübingen - development of Website and of the new Corporate Design, Project together with D. Hundertmark.
